EXCITING NEWS! We have partnered with London’s leading Make-up & Hair training Academy @delamaracademy to host an exciting competition. BUT there's a catch...we want YOU to be the judges! 

Over the next week, starting on Sunday 5th and ending Monday 13th June, we will be posting an array of stunning eye make-up looks created and photographed by Delamar's talented young students and we want YOU to choose your favourite. 

5 looks will be posted every other day, and we need you to cast your vote in the comments! The winner will be decided based on the total number of votes their image receives once all the looks have been posted so make sure to like and share your favourite look. 

Our winner will receive a full BY TERRY make-up kit to start them on their MUA journey. 

Start your engines, may the best Make-up Artist win!
